<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> <!-- Important for mobile responsiveness -->
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            margin: auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: block;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .table-responsive {
            width: 100%;
            overflow-x: auto; /* Allows horizontal scrolling */
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; /* Smooth scrolling for iOS */
            scrollbar-width: thin; /* For Firefox */
            scrollbar-color: #008ce3 #f4f4f4; /* Custom scrollbar color for Firefox */
        }
        .table-responsive table {
            width: 100%;
            min-width: 600px; /* Prevent column squish */
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        table, th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        th, td {
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #e2e2e2;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #008ce3;
            color: white;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 1px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #888;
        }

        /* For webkit browsers (Chrome, Safari) to ensure scrollbars are visible */
        .table-responsive::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 12px; /* Width of the scrollbar */
        }
        .table-responsive::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background-color: #008ce3; /* Color of the scrollbar thumb */
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        .table-responsive::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background-color: #f4f4f4; /* Color of the scrollbar track */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dydfwvvro/image/upload/fl_preserve_transparency/v1746507037/arc-cc_mrkifp.jpg" alt="ArcOne" class="logo">

        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Please find below the details of pending cheque in hand:</p>

            <div class="table-responsive">
                <div style="display: block; overflow-x: auto;">
                    {{{chequeTables}}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            Best regards,<br>
            ArcOne Team
            <p>This is a system generated email. Please do not reply, as responses to this email are not monitored.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
